    </div>
</div>

<div class="container py-5 text-white">
    <div class="row text-center">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <i class="fas fa-cogs fa-3x mb-3"></i>
            <h3>Powerful Framework</h3>
            <p>ASP.NET Core is a powerful framework for building dynamic web applications.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
